main event: A witness observed an unidentified object in Burbank, California on July 17, 1965.
interesting points: The object appeared to be large and was observed on a hazy day,The witness described the object as round or disc-shaped,The object was estimated to be moving fairly fast at 35 to 40 mph,It was about 1/2 mile away when observed,The analysis concluded that the objects were likely a double image caused by reflection.
